---
import Link from "./ui/link.astro";
---

<section class="relative left-1/2 right-1/2 ml-[-50vw] mr-[-50vw] w-screen py-20 px-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-primary)] to-[var(--color-primary-dark)] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center fadein-section">
  <h2 class="text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Únete a nuestras reuniones exclusivas</h2>
  <p class="text-white/80 text-lg md:text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Completa el formulario a continuación para aplicar a nuestras reuniones de desayuno. Conéctate directamente con tomadores de decisiones y acelera tu crecimiento.</p>
  <Link href="#" class="flex gap-1 items-center justify-center bg-white text-[var(--color-primary)] px-5 py-2 rounded font-semibold hover:bg-[var(--color-primary)] hover:text-white transition">
  <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
  Aplicar
</Link>
</section>
